      "properties": {
        "text": "Seedance2.0 real person material mode\\n\\nFlow:\\n1. image1 stays on the normal direct-upload path\\n2. image2 and video1 are pre-converted to Seedance2.0 assets because real_person_mode=true and conversion_slots=image2,video1\\n3. If asset creation fails for image2 or video1, that slot automatically falls back to the original upload path\\n\\nNotes:\\n- real_person_mode only affects local IMAGE / VIDEO slots on the 4 Seedance2.0 / Seedance2.0-Fast image-capable nodes\\n- conversion_slots=all converts every supported image/video slot\\n- asset_ids can still be connected at the same time for manually managed assets"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
